-retired)</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Mirriana_00</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Aye, I forgot about the fright forged helm.  Almost as good as ethereal, so you can wear it a lot.  But, you wouldn't believe how much time I have spent looking for Kalayia.  I got the other quest pieces, then the person in Paineel ate the helm ones.  I love my shield and mask, but the helm just takes too much.  I'm sure I've logged on my tracker 40 times in LFay and haven't seen her again.  Many times just after a patch.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
